Welcome to the HRBreazeApplication  project!

this appliation takes the existing Durandal Single Page Application (SPA) project in ASP.NET MVC and adds in Server-side Authentication using the built-in Simple Membership and OAUTH membership included in the .NET 4.0 & 4.5 Frameworks.


its  a good sample to use breaze and memberships ,its an SPA application build on Durandal


in this application we are using a many views to see you how can you use the SPA in a big projects


